<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.2.3">
<l>emmā ṉumemmaṉaiyu meṉṉaippeṟ ṟoḻintataṟpiṉ</l>
<l>ammā ṉumammaṉaiyu maṭiyēṉuk kākiniṉṟa</l>
<l>naṉmā ṉavoṇcuṭarē naṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampīyuṉ</l>
<l>maimmā ṉavaṇṇamallāl makiḻntētta māṭṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Brilliant light like virtue who endures, having become father and mother</l>
<l>For me, [your] servant, after my father and mother,</l>
<l>Having begotten me, left, O noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr,</l>
<l>Besides your form like ink, I will not joyfully praise [any].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
